{"tid":1559404,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"免費安全 大學生 VPN教學（多圖，簡易）","createTime":"2019-09-10T19:49:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T11:27:58.000Z","uid":156828,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ff362b85799db8e800c408acf5c0306d0680ae1e","tid":1559404,"uid":156828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T19:49:15.000Z","msg":"此教學來自台灣的一位朋友，使用平台 Azure portal，有見香港現況，經台灣朋友同意下，決定作為it狗出一分力，比大家可以用VPN玩日本手遊(如公主連接)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">使用Azure原因</span></strong></span>：Azure係Microsoft 旗下，Microsoft有100$USD quota比學生ac（<a href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/zh-tw/free/students/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fazure.microsoft.com%2Fzh-tw%2Ffree%2Fstudents%2F&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRegwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=698d055e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://azure.microsoft.com/zh-tw/free/students/</a>)<br />\n你需要用大學生Office365使用既ac（中學生好似都有，但我唔肯定Azure有沒 e.g. <span style=\"color: red;\">a0000000@live.ouhk.edu.hk</span>），同時會有各種服務同軟件，我就唔一一介紹了<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>1.建vm linux&amp;\u0016\u0016\u0016使用linux建 Debian</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n進入Azure Portal <a href=\"https://portal.azure.com/#home\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fportal.azure.com%2F%23home&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRegwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=39e2f3df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://portal.azure.com/#home</a> ,打開azure cloud shell,下圖圈住既位置,按一下建立儲存體<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7yxr1EJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7yxr1EJ.png&h=f438498d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n使用<a href=\"http://codepad.org/TxbGhBr1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcodepad.org%2FTxbGhBr1&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRegwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=75a8fffb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://codepad.org/TxbGhBr1</a> ，先copy and paste az group create......,後copy and paste az vm create\\...\\...\\...\\...\\...\\...,完成後畫面如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qsGwtpg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqsGwtpg.png&h=1eb0a825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">--admin-username = 你喜歡的username<br />\n--admin-password = 你的密碼 需要12-72個字</span> <br />\n</span>  <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>2. Debian IP更改為靜態</strong></span><br />\n首先，按所有資源，再按DebianPublic，出現下圖畫面，按組態，靜態，儲存<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8umcXnG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8umcXnG.png&h=7586e372&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n更改為靜態ip可以保持ip唔會因為重開而改變，改變ip教學會於post內補上教學<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>3. Debian 硬碟SSD 轉HDD</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n由於default開啟會配SSD，但SSD係收費，而HDD 30GB係免費，所以我們要改配置<br />\n<br />\n首先，按所有資源，再按Debian，出現下圖畫面，按停止，答&quot;是&quot;，然後按磁碟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0xCPfcJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0xCPfcJ.png&h=5d0bf8cc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n入到去得一個比你選，按Debian_OsDisk_1_XXXXXXXXXXXX，同樣有組態可以選擇，按組態進入以下畫面，更改SSD為HDD<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3rS339D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3rS339D.png&h=73d03222&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n更改完後回到Debian，按<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 啟動</span></strong>"},{"pid":"c849654af8705d2b94aad0c68a97ab906331b8bb","tid":1559404,"uid":156828,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T19:54:02.000Z","msg":"不停失敗點貼...."},{"pid":"afb28a52890f2d87da167233287998199777373e","tid":1559404,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:19:53.000Z","msg":"Google Cloud 送 usd300"},{"pid":"8a10b38f6e7800cab3e76f6eae3125c891a5dc29","tid":1559404,"uid":155781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:31:23.000Z","msg":"GCP<img src=\"/a